history.content:
Dear Students,

Sometimes students are concerned or have questions about what is in their Academic Progress Report on Calcentral, APR.  If you have questions about it you can email us:  cs-advising@cs.berkeley.edu  *You don't need to make a full appointment for this*  The APR is a great tool but occasionally it does need updating and fixes and advisors can do this as needed/appropriate.  

*Remember too that any questions about Letters and Science requirements on APR need to go to them:  asklns@berkeley.edu  or go to their virtual front desk.
history.subject: From Advising:  If you ever have questions/concerns about APR you can email us
